News Village Appoints Van Orden Controller
Dec 22, 2011









SPRINGFIELD, N.J. — John L. Van Orden has been appointed to serve as the controller and principal accounting officer of Village Super Market here, the company said in a government filing.

	The company's previous principal accounting officer, Kevin Begley, continues to serve as Village's principal financial officer, treasurer and director.





